originalText.text: (WORST EXPERIENCE EVER.) I waited over three hours, for a nerve test and was never called. Waisted time. They perform botox procedures in this location. So if you are paying in cash for botox, then they will take care of you first. Even though the other person has medical insurance, and a appointment that was scheduled two months ago. I should had read the reviews before scheduling a appointment. I'm sure this is illegal as well.
